Martin B. Anstice 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at LAM RESEARCH CORP, Martin B. Anstice  made $10,556,031 in total compensation.  Of this total $937,789 was received as a salary, $2,207,558 was received as a bonus, $1,224,848 was received in stock options, $6,175,315 was awarded as stock and $10,521 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


